# Interactive Marketing Sphere (Next.js)

Glossy 3D sphere with three islands:
- **Entertainment Nation** (movies, short films, games)
- **Product Peninsula** (gadgets and products)
- **Clothing Continent** (apparel)

Click a marker to open a **left-side pop-up** with a link to the product/site.

## Quick start (locally)
```bash
npm install
npm run dev
